'' ``{c}Zeta`` is project collaboration application''
using Linux server, web and your browser as the platform. \\ 
The application has reached beta stage and is being contantly improved for
perfomance, stability and usability.
* Feel free to explore the application in 
  [[ http://sandbox.devwhiz.net | sandbox environment ]]
* ''[[ /help/features | Features offered ]]''
* '' [[ /help/zwiki/ZWiki | ZWiki ]] '', wiki engine that powers zeta
  documents.
* [[ mailto:support@discoverzeta.com | contact ]].

=== __Highlights__

